examples.en: She claims that she was framed.
The two men were framed for murder.
I didn't do the job, I've been framed up.
Her face was framed in a mass of red hair.
He is framed to be a soldier.
The innocent man was framed by the police.
The photographs will look nice framed in black.
He stood, a threatening figure, framed in the doorway.
I'm going to get the picture framed.
Sarah's face was framed by her long dark hair.
He framed his honorable discharge from the army.
We gave them a framed family photo for their anniversary.
The city is framed by mountain ranges to the east and west.
The family's theory was that the cheating businessmen somehow framed their brother.
A few tendrils of hair framed her face.
